For a gentle introduction to Crux, please see the Crux 
home page under the doc directory at home-tutorial.html 
or at http://noble.gs.washington.edu/proj/crux/.

For installation instructions, see the install-tutorial.html 
linked from the Crux home pages listed above, or the INSTALL
file in this directory.

Crux source code can be found in the src/c sub-directory.
